data.description: SELLER CONTRIBUTION!! $6K toward closing or interest rate buy down!! Opportunity to assume the loan at 4.25%!!* Walking distance to area schools in a neighborhood where children still ride their bikes to school. This gently loved home is conveniently located near toll road I-30 between Austin and San Antonio. Built in 2021 by reputable KB Homes, it's floor plan is suitable to host many fun gatherings. Upstairs is a flex room, which can be made into a media room, play room, or office. Enjoy your coffee while watching the sunrise in cozy nook in the master suite. Look no further! There is a plenty space for everyone in this home. Electricity ranges  $147-$187 month for the current home owners.* Some photos are virtually staged.
